<section id="download" class="download bg-primary text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10" style="margin: 0 auto;">
              <div class="section-heading mb-5">
                  <h2>Find Your Pivot Power</h2>
                  <hr>
              </div>
                <h3>Change won’t stop. Can you keep up?</h3>
                <p>Frenzied transformations in work and life have created a range of new opportunities, but have also left many people disoriented and struggling to regain power over their lives.</p>
                <p>In the past, people could be reasonably confident of achieving success through a path of getting a degree, getting hired, and climbing that employer’s ladder. But the rapid pace of change in work and life means that we can’t expect such sure, linear paths to success.</p>

                <h3>To succeed amid change, you need a different kind of preparation.</h3>
                <p>Today, your chances for economic security and advancement depend on not being reliant on a single path, but being able to reposition yourself and make many new plays, or pivots, across your lifetime.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="steps" class="features">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <div class="section-heading">
                    <h2>Having Pivot Power means you’re able to:</h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <!-- <i class="icon fa fa-life-ring text-primary"></i> -->
                                <h3>Broaden the Field</h3>
                                <p class="text-muted">You have an expansive sense of what is possible for you, can continue to build new skills, envision many ways to repackage your core strengths, and have diverse networks to link you to many opportunities</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <!-- <i class="icon fa fa-star text-primary"></i> -->
                                <h3>Make a Play</h3>
                                <p class="text-muted">Even when success is uncertain, you are willing to take action, can financially invest in your future, and learn from failure to create success</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-item">
                                <!-- <i class="icon fa fa-share-alt text-primary"></i> -->
                                <h3>Shift, Not Drift</h3>
                                <p class="text-muted">You don’t just change to whatever new opportunity is available, but act purposefully out of a core sense of yourself and clarity of what is important to you, so that each each pivot is not just a move, but a move forward</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                        <p>To build that Pivot Power, we help you identify what you most want and value and what your core value creation strengths are that you can use to pursue those things. Then we assess the mental, social, and financial assets you have that give you greater power to pivot. Finally we connect you to information and networks to better equip you to pivot.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="contact" class="features contact bg-blue bg-primary">
