          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6" style="margin: 0 auto;">
            <ul class="text-left">
              <li><h4><strong>Core Self</strong></h4>Do you have a strong sense of your own value that is resilient to changing circumstances and can guide your action?</li>
              <li><h4><strong>Expansive Self</strong></h4>Are you able to envision a range of possibilities for yourself?</li>
              <li><h4><strong>Enterprising Self</strong></h4>Do you have an opportunity-seeking, problem-solving mental orientation, with a bias toward action, and an ability to see take from failure the seeds of success?</li>
